---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import HeaderTop from "../components/HeaderTop";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.vue";

import Social from "../components/Social.svelte";
---

<Layout title="about">
	<HeaderTop client:load />
	<section class="pt-20">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-3xl">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl text-purple-500">Sobre Mí</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
				<div class="rounded-xl relative h-64 overflow-hidden sm:h-80 lg:h-full">
					<img
						alt="IA avatar"
						src="../../public/images/City-Lights.png"
						class="rounded-xl w-full h-full md:w-90 md:h-100 inset-0 lg:w-full lg:object-cover object-contain"
					/>
				</div>

				<div class="lg:py-16">
					<article class="space-y-4 text-white">
						<h3 class="text-2xl">
							Escritora por pasión, developer por prefesión.
						</h3>

						<p>
							Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Non dolores maxime provident, dolorum sapiente, eaque corrupti sint blanditiis placeat, iusto exercitationem porro recusandae vero! Voluptatem id in reiciendis exercitationem odio!
						</p>
						<p>
							Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi beatae molestiae corporis consectetur, voluptatem officia consequuntur sed sunt veniam minima? Harum sapiente nemo inventore quae. Beatae vel necessitatibus totam assumenda.
						</p>
						<Social />
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<Footer />
	</section>
</Layout>
